description: Proposed demolition of all existing buildings and construction of part five / part six / part seven / part eight / part nine storey buildings comprising 136 residential units (Use Class C3, comprising of 42 x 1 bed, 56 x 2 bed and 38 x 3 bed flats) and community/retail floorspace (Use Classes D1/A1/A3); related lower ground car park comprising 44 car parking spaces; cycle parking, vehicular access; footways; landscaping; plant and associated works  and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 21 July 2017 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended.
